      "source": "https://www.townofrotterdam.gov/our-town/town-history"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "When the Erie Canal opened in 1825, nearby hamlets such as Rotterdam Junction sprang up along its banks.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        11
